<h2>About <%= siteData.siteName %></h2>

<p>VocationConnect is a platform designed to bridge the gap between current students and alumni, facilitating mentorship, career guidance, and interview preparation.</p>

<h3>Our Mission</h3>
<p>To empower students with real-world career insights and interview practice opportunities through meaningful connections with experienced alumni professionals.</p>

<h3>Key Features</h3>
<ul class="features-list">
  <li><strong>Alumni Network:</strong> Access a diverse network of alumni across various industries and companies</li>
  <li><strong>Mock Interview Platform:</strong> Conduct realistic interview simulations with video, chat, and note-taking capabilities</li>
  <li><strong>Mentorship Opportunities:</strong> Build lasting connections with alumni mentors</li>
  <li><strong>Career Guidance:</strong> Get personalized advice on career paths, job searching, and professional development</li>
</ul>

<h3>Technology Stack</h3>
<ul class="features-list">
  <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js with Express framework</li>
  <li><strong>Database:</strong> MySQL for robust data management</li>
  <li><strong>Templating:</strong> EJS for dynamic content rendering</li>
  <li><strong>Security:</strong> bcrypt password hashing and session-based authentication</li>
  <li><strong>Real-time Features:</strong> WebRTC for video communication (integrated)</li>
</ul>

<h3>For Students</h3>
<p>Gain confidence in your interview skills, learn about different career paths, and receive guidance from professionals who have been in your shoes.</p>

<h3>For Alumni</h3>
<p>Give back to your alma mater, help shape the next generation of professionals, and stay connected with your university community.</p>
